### 1.整数定义域的二分
```
int DRHPSY(int L,int R)
{
    int L=1,R=n,ans;
    while(L<=R)
{
    int mid=(L+R)>>1;
    if(check(mid))ans=mid,L=mid+1;
       else R=mid-1;
}
    return ans;
}
```
